{"tid":2136460,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[巨大挑戰] C.朗拿度：祖記奪冠看似容易其實不然 明年要拿第3冠","createTime":"2020-08-02T07:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T10:26:40.000Z","uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9daaad2731089ae88a3d31e271457c63232644ce","tid":2136460,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"儘管在意甲收官戰中1-3輸給了羅馬，但祖記還是憑藉1分的優勢，捧起了意甲聯賽的冠軍獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n  今場比賽C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）並沒有進入大名單，但他依然和隊友們在賽後一起參加了頒獎典禮，捧起了冠軍獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n  賽後C.朗拿度也在ins上發出了一張祖記全隊慶祝奪冠的照片，並配文稱：「很開心能作為祖記一員，參與球隊9連冠中的2冠！奪冠看上去很輕鬆但實際上並非如此！你需要足夠有天賦、努力訓練，展現出自己的水平，要年複一年的做到這些，這樣才能達到你的目標，比之前做得更好！讓我們為我的第3次奪冠而努力吧！」"},{"pid":"16015eea22b331670ff25d9f746238657a45c967","tid":2136460,"uid":90515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"10連冠大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca54350b101be5d7ae229bec792bfcbfc80a49f","tid":2136460,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16015eea22b331670ff25d9f746238657a45c967","tid":2136460,"uid":90515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"10連冠大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fe54c9d31d7795a8bd6f8e4fb868048ba21e6b","tid":2136460,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"唔係去拜，psg"},{"pid":"6ec25304084b2ab42561582687e9cf451ba41ff8","tid":2136460,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"的確唔易<br />\n<br />\n如果贏唔到意甲<br />\n會被人恥笑"},{"pid":"aeb6078f0ce2677f2b531f75fc9b7fd5512d8c89","tid":2136460,"uid":90515,"like":0,"disl